This JSON file represents a Jupyter Notebook with cells for exploratory data analysis of the IMDB 50K sentiment dataset. It includes cells for dataset overview, review length distribution plot, sentiment balance bar chart, word clouds for positive and negative reviews, top 20 most common words, and summary findings.

To use this notebook, replace `'path_to_your_imdb_dataset'` with the actual path to your IMDB dataset. The notebook assumes that the dataset is in a directory with two subdirectories, one for positive reviews and one for negative reviews.

Please note that you need to have the necessary libraries installed (pandas, numpy, matplotlib, wordcloud, seaborn, scikit-learn) to run this notebook. Also, make sure that the IMDB dataset is in the correct format and location.